OL,3,CAndrew RT Davies' exit signals start
OL,4,Cof ideological battle for Welsh Tories
OL,6,FIt began with a traffic jam.
OL,8,FAndrew RT Davies found himself stuck
OL,9,Fon his way into Cardiff Bay, delaying
OL,10,Fthe start of a meeting which would
OL,11,Fdecide his political fate.
OL,13,FThe Senedd Conservative leader entered
OL,14,Fthe room knowing full well his
OL,15,Fcolleagues were already divided over
OL,16,Fhis leadership.
