OL,3,CAndrew RT Davies' exit signals start
OL,4,Cof ideological battle for Welsh Tories
OL,6,FLast week, he was informed that seven
OL,7,Fmembers of his shadow cabinet were
OL,8,Fprepared to resign unless he
OL,9,Freconsidered his position. In
OL,10,Fresponse, he met with them to hear
OL,11,Ftheir concerns.
OL,13,FConservative sources say it was
OL,14,Fsuggested Andrew RT Davies step down
OL,15,F"on his own terms" to preserve his
OL,16,Fdignity. But he pushed back,
OL,17,Fquestioning how that could happen when
OL,18,Fsome within the group had leaked their
OL,19,Fplans to the media.
