OL,3,CAndrew RT Davies' exit signals start
OL,4,Cof ideological battle for Welsh Tories
OL,6,FUltimately, he chose to take control
OL,7,Fof the situation, declaring that he
OL,8,Fwould call a vote of confidence in his
OL,9,Fleadership.
OL,11,FAs the meeting began, expectations
OL,12,Fwere that a secret ballot would be
OL,13,Fheld. Instead, Andrew RT Davies
OL,14,Fproposed a show of hands, a motion
OL,15,Fwhich was seconded. Now, there would
OL,16,Fbe no hiding: everyone would know who
OL,17,Fwanted to back him or sack him.
