OL,3,CAndrew RT Davies' exit signals start
OL,4,Cof ideological battle for Welsh Tories
OL,6,FAfter the vote, Andrew RT Davies
OL,7,Fconsulted with some MS colleagues,
OL,8,FRussell George, former leader Paul
OL,9,FDavies, and chief whip Darren Millar.
OL,10,FThey agreed he should stay on as
OL,11,Finterim leader. He informed the group
OL,12,Fand published a letter to the Welsh
OL,13,FTory chair setting out his plan.
OL,15,FConservative sources have described
OL,16,Fthe atmosphere since his announcement
OL,17,Fas "gloomy".
