OL,3,CAndrew RT Davies' exit signals start
OL,4,Cof ideological battle for Welsh Tories
OL,6,F"Sometimes it is difficult to accept
OL,7,Fwhen your time is up in politics,"
OL,8,Fsaid one. "Andrew's frustration at
OL,9,Flosing the top job is clear. In time
OL,10,Fhe'll recognise he made the best
OL,11,Fdecision for the party with the next
OL,12,Felection 18 months away."
OL,14,FBut is that it? No, it's clear this is
OL,15,Fthe start of a bigger ideological
OL,16,Fbattle within the Welsh Conservative
OL,17,Fmovement. At stake is the party's
OL,18,Ffuture direction and Wales' politics.
