OL,3,CAndrew RT Davies' exit signals start
OL,4,Cof ideological battle for Welsh Tories
OL,6,FHowever, supporters of Andrew RT
OL,7,FDavies have a warning for the so-
OL,8,Fcalled "plotters": if they win, they
OL,9,Fshouldn't expect any more loyalty than
OL,10,Fthey've shown to him.
OL,12,FOne last question - what's next for RT?
OL,14,FWhile he's ruled out defecting to
OL,15,FReform, could that stance shift? If
OL,16,Fdiscontented with the direction under
OL,17,Fthe next leader, might he follow the
OL,18,Fpath of other Conservative politicians
OL,19,Fand make the leap, handing Nigel
OL,20,FFarage a coup and fracturing the
OL,21,FConservative Party?
